# Sound Button Component - Use SoundButton Only

**Always use `SoundButton`** from `@/components/sound/sound-button` for displaying sound buttons. Never use the icon-based `CompactSoundButton` from `@/components/blog/CompactSoundButton`.

## Rules

- **DO** use: `import SoundButton from "@/components/sound/sound-button"`
- **DON'T** use: `import CompactSoundButton from "@/components/blog/CompactSoundButton"` (shows Volume2 icon instead of proper button)

## Usage

```tsx
// Correct - SoundButton shows the 3D styled button
import SoundButton from "@/components/sound/sound-button"

<SoundButton
  sound={sound}
  customSize={80}
  hideActions
  isAboveTheFold={index < 4}
/>
```

## Props

- `sound`: Sound type (from `@/lib/types/sound`) - ProcessedSound from API maps directly
- `customSize`: Optional - e.g. 64, 80 for compact grids
- `hideActions`: Optional - hide like/download for compact layouts
- `hideLabel`: Optional - hide sound name below button
- `isAboveTheFold`: Optional - for above-fold optimization

## Wrong

```tsx
// Wrong - uses generic Volume2 icon
import CompactSoundButton from "@/components/blog/CompactSoundButton"
<CompactSoundButton sound={sound} />
```
